半刻面多面體的特性也意味著部份面會通過多面體的幾何中心，並互相相交。<ref name="gailiunasfinite"/>這個立體在視覺外觀上，每個正方形被分成四個直角三角形，但只有2個直角三角形可見，其餘被三角形面遮蔽。<ref name="software3d Tetrahemi"/>

=== 頂點座標 ===
這個立體共享了[[正八面體|正八面體]]的頂點排列方式<ref name="software3d Tetrahemi"/>，因此其頂點座標與[[正八面體|正八面體]]相同<ref name="dmccooeydata Octahedron">{{Cite web|url=http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/Octahedron.txt|title=Data of Octahedron | author=David I. McCooey | year=2015|publisher=dmccooey.com|access-date=2021-07-30|archive-date=2021-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210730100840/http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/Octahedron.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dmccooeydata Tetrahemihexahedron">{{Cite web|url=http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/Tetrahemihexahedron.txt|title=Data of Tetrahemihexahedron | author=David I. McCooey | year=2015|publisher=dmccooey.com|access-date=2021-07-30|archive-date=2018-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180411192839/http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/Tetrahemihexahedron.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite Mathworld|title= Regular Octahedron|urlname=RegularOctahedron}}</ref>：
: ( ±1, 0, 0 );
: ( 0, ±1, 0 );
: ( 0, 0, ±1 ).
