=== 定向性 ===
四面半六面體的表面是一個不可[[可定向性|定向]]的曲面<ref name= "Regular Map Hemi-cuboctahedron"/>，即無法定義表面上特定點屬於內部或外部，因為任何點都可以在不打洞的情況下經由表面找到一個路徑連接該點對應的背面的位置，這個特性與[[克萊因瓶|克萊因瓶]]類似<ref name= "home.xs4all.nl"/>。四面半六面體是唯一一種歐拉特徵數為1的均勻多面體<ref name= "home.xs4all.nl" >{{cite web | url = https://westy31.home.xs4all.nl/SalvagedGooglePlus/SalvagedGooglePlus_Part2.html | title = The Tetrahemihexahedron | publisher = home.xs4all.nl | accessdate = 2021-07-24 | archive-date = 2021-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210610075744/http://westy31.home.xs4all.nl/SalvagedGooglePlus/SalvagedGooglePlus_Part2.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，故其為投影多面體，其在[[实射影平面|实射影平面]]上生成的曲面與{{link-en|羅馬曲面|Roman surface}}類似。<ref name="P. Gailiunas_2018">{{cite journal| title=Polyhedral Models of the Projective Plane| journal=Bridges 2018 Conference Proceedings| author=P. Gailiunas| year=2018| url=https://archive.bridgesmathart.org/2018/bridges2018-543.pdf| access-date=2021-07-30| archive-date=2021-08-31| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210831205922/https://archive.bridgesmathart.org/2018/bridges2018-543.pdf}}</ref>
