皮特里八面體與[[正八面體|正八面體]]互為[[皮特里對偶|皮特里對偶]]，也就是說，皮特里八面體的皮特里對偶為[[正八面體|正八面體]]，換句話說，即皮特里八面體的[[皮特里多邊形|皮特里多邊形]]為[[正三角形|正三角形]]<ref name= "Regular Map Petrial octahedron"/><ref name= "Regular Map octahedron" >{{cite web | url = http://www.weddslist.com/rmdb/map.php?a=R0.2 | title = The octahedron | publisher = Regular Map database - map details | accessdate = 2021-07-30 | archive-date = 2021-07-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210730134242/http://www.weddslist.com/rmdb/map.php?a=R0.2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

拓樸結構與皮特里八面體互相對應的[[正則地區圖|正則地區圖]]其在施萊夫利符號中可以用{6,4}表示，其意義代表每個頂點都是4個六邊形的公共頂點。相同的拓樸結構可透過將[[正四面體|正四面體]]的頂點所有替換成{{link-en|交叉蓋|Cross-cap}}，並且將所有稜替換為四價頂點，同時將所有面替換成邊數為原來邊數兩倍的面來構成。<ref name= "Regular Map Petrial octahedron"/><ref name= "Regular Map Full Shurikens" >{{cite web | url = http://www.weddslist.com/rmdb/pages/relations/shu.php#full | title = Full Shurikens | publisher = Regular Map database, weddslist.com | accessdate = 2021-07-30 | archive-date = 2020-08-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807153706/http://www.weddslist.com/rmdb/pages/relations/shu.php#full | dead-url = no }}</ref>其對應的對偶多面體在施萊夫利符號中可以用{4,6}表示，其意義代表每個頂點都是6個四邊形的公共頂點，並具有6個面、12條邊和4個頂點<ref name= "Regular Map dual of petrial octahedron" >{{cite web | url = http://www.weddslist.com/rmdb/map.php?a=N4.2 | title = C4:{4,6}<sub>3</sub> | publisher=Regular Map database - map details | accessdate=2021-07-30}}</ref>。
